{"tid":1630213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登要開始成熟啦！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:26:34.000Z","uid":76543,"like":175,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f3895c08aabddc960491a52a78132544e2dab3","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"做錯咗就要認 今日掟中記者一定要道歉<br />\n你當做好文宣 形象咩都好 一定要認錯<br />\n唔好話咩黑警做嘅 卧底做嘅 我哋唔清楚<br />\n但係大家深知我哋tk到記者機會都大嘅<br />\n咁做人係錯就要認 呢啲係良知<br />\n唔好話咩黑警錯都唔認啦 呢個正正係我哋同佢哋嘅分別<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋仲係人仲有良知呀！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人要一齊贏呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"bf178987523df9795764522b106304b75bffaf7c","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"44a5be185d9b0c9e99bfcb1d0ae748915931f463","tid":1630213,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:47:47.000Z","msg":"有用post永遠推唔到<br />\n大家幫下小弟手可以嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［緊急幫推］可唔可以搵文宣組即時整18區開花poster<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630136</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"be8ae47ac2c95ad40ed3f21b6100f39c141832a5","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:47:48.000Z","msg":"民間記者會幫手道一道歉"},{"pid":"c918ab21c6ca915ebce5f78e98e13d032f2a90bd","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:47:58.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"e6fce96bf2dbf972a57ab48f38583d1fd351fbb8","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"c20948da8b2900868919510b67af8180b585c9ed","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"3b5b8946ca2b7c6c8d447e31dca89a9527af651e","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"3db9e4f4d647a60eb8ff5ad8190bfc643cd6ed51","tid":1630213,"uid":130079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"c61fdbd05888846dfd8930b5e3531b5e6ad0cda3","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:41.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"ff7a9a2e239bfee427677a05e3e8202530608430","tid":1630213,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da72d33625bb9ff9d072e9982438611c31d49ea2","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:52.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"faff7305bfcb76a2cf705e2709776960cbd0e98e","tid":1630213,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:02.000Z","msg":"RTHK 已澄清"},{"pid":"1afe824a22e90e9d5da85eac0ceea016f7b03764","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"4eec31dac5a5dcb42150b228272567f7b71bb064","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"459cfac8bb2f9091e083fc3ea2478a0934fb23c8","tid":1630213,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47064e0dd369dff119ed17da840386937f90658c","tid":1630213,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"be humble, don't lie like blue c"},{"pid":"ca4fc10926418fed3f8d9f96561ac3db5c473be1","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:23.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b7c8134afdd1e8198bf1ad8cc469fe024d6a7216","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:33.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"83145128472501ca30e17a3467bbc2e161a3190b","tid":1630213,"uid":76543,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"faff7305bfcb76a2cf705e2709776960cbd0e98e","tid":1630213,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:02.000Z","msg":"RTHK 已澄清"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"咁我哋都要為做錯嘢而道歉"},{"pid":"eff81ab59e6d1208bf95f79ea90d27a4dc828ef0","tid":1630213,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c